TikTok Rewards is TikTok's official referral program and our way of saying thank you to our amazing community of users! 

When you invite friends to join you on TikTok you can get points to redeem for gift cards or donate to local charities. 

To get started, simply go to your Profile and tap the rewards icon in the top left corner. From there you can send your invite code to friends, browse rewards and donation options, and redeem points. 

For more information and eligibility information check out https://www.tiktok.com/tiktok-rewards/program-overview/.
